app.controllers

Class TaskController

  • java.lang.Object
    • app.controllers.TaskController

  • public class TaskController
extends java.lang.Object
    In charge of sorting and searching of tasks. Actual sorting of tasks is done in Model Manager, this just acts as an interface to that. Implemented as a singleton.
